{
  "stem": "15393.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Scholastica, which was a Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] there were no Jewish children at that school, being a Catholic school, obviously.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he had his eye on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was no swaying him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and-- and he did manage to get me, even though they-- with all the nos that-- that were on the list, not only starting with my age, but also being Jewish and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That did not [SIGHS] make things easier, put it this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he proved to them what he wanted to prove.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they accepted me to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I went to that school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a very rigoristic school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was-- one had to be dressed in a specific fashion, a special type of uniform, on top of which, there was a white overall.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And if there was the slightest, slightest stain, one was punished this way or another for it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had slippers, which were felt lined, so that we weren't-- we weren't heard walking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And also, we wouldn't scratch the beautifully, beautifully shiny parquet floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that sort of-- that sort of school, it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't know if I was happy or unhappy in this school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I can't tell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was going to school, and that was interesting enough.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it wasn't far from home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I walked to school every day on my own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Not something one could easily do today, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On one occasion, some-- we-- I had a very, very unpleasant experience, which stayed in my mind, very vividly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you'd like me to tell you about it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, it was a Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were three Jewish girls in it, to the best of my knowledge, only.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
